{"tid":45379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"炒樓夫婦好勵志！ 憑8.5萬六年變做千萬富翁","createTime":"2016-12-19T02:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T03:58:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a60b57d6d1cc3b5ff26ab51759daf46f9233bbfb","tid":45379,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"炒樓夫婦好勵志！ 憑8.5萬六年變做千萬富翁<br />\n<br />\n30歲前就可以辭去工作，經營自己的生意？澳洲80後奧尼爾夫婦（Scott and Mina O'Neill）不是富二代亦沒有中大獎，他們當初僅以1.5萬澳元（8.5萬港元）投資房地產，現時擁有的物業佈滿澳洲，估計價值1,000萬澳元（5,679萬港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n奧尼爾夫婦2010年分別年僅22歲和23歲時，在悉尼南部首次置業，樓價為48萬澳元（272萬港元），他們坦言首次買屋的錢是省吃儉用得來。 <br />\n<br />\n奧尼爾太太指「上車」是最困難，隨後就越來越容易，「當你買第一間物業，舉例說你以40萬澳元（227萬港元）買入，數年後升值至50萬澳元（283萬港元），你就可以去銀行再融資樓價升幅的80%，即8萬澳元（45萬港元），再用作買另一間屋的首期，從而『錢搵錢』。」 <br />\n<br />\n兩人6年來不斷買入物業，現時擁有25間房屋。近年澳洲樓價飆升，2010年在薩瑟蘭（Sutherland）一間房屋只需50萬澳元（283萬港元），現值84萬澳元（477萬港元），令他們身家暴升，他們亦從不賣出物業，只將單住放租。 <br />\n<br />\n兩人又指，不會考慮租金回報低過6%的房屋，以確保租金可以抵消供樓貸款。他們又告誡年輕人，投資目光要放遠全國，不可以只着眼自己的社區。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161218/large/1482056669_9caa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161218%2Flarge%2F1482056669_9caa.jpg&h=11650620&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1367b3b8597c1800a8ee399a98387befcd206ccf","tid":45379,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:40:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ec0f7790a31cb7ee01679a2dac99fe621a599b","tid":45379,"uid":46373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"一個地震玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2905178dd12afd97c9fab74045180236011f062b","tid":45379,"uid":2674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:48:19.000Z","msg":"講真佢地唔算炒喎<br />\n淨係買同放租，係真係食正樓市升緊條水"},{"pid":"6ff5215ca04d92ad0695b9f4271ed5586df5ff58","tid":45379,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"外國人炒樓=醒"},{"pid":"03660fc43036d0997bcc9f6a6323e50ad4f3413b","tid":45379,"uid":46139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:55:44.000Z","msg":"鬼佬唔識嘢先覺得佢醒。97有條友又係咁樣炒嘉湖山莊幾十個單位，樓市一跌，即刻破產"},{"pid":"d2eae32f16228a8b4cc7405fea0db818a05269fd","tid":45379,"uid":46139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"樓價跌租金都會跌。佢以為而家租金cover到，到時樓價跌，俾人夾死，明知跌過籠，幾錢都要賤賣"},{"pid":"5e40a7a9d3d628b8e8ce27cfec2a528c16aba848","tid":45379,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"今日ge世界, 知識 能力 勞動力 產業 都已經不再重要<br />\n只剩低投機 炒賣同虛擬產業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信下一步 淪陷ge就係道德同信任"},{"pid":"c58a4a0a5105305280b8d7e15f9e17408b55d8e7","tid":45379,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外國人炒樓=醒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔賣叫唔叫炒？"},{"pid":"b0eda6e416c382f372016a261c3cb3aa8ff2ac91","tid":45379,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:03:47.000Z","msg":"因為依家低息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a721df3fb989eae25e08aae4142dd7033c3202ba","tid":45379,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個地震玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21361ddb2d9c4e73326075788273caf6740343b1","tid":45379,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個地震玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個世界末日 全世界有錢佬都玩完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor